### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### GET All Pitches (Canchas)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pitchs/getAll

### GET One Pitch by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/pitchs/getOne/1

### POST - Add New Pitch (requiere autenticación admin o business_owner)
# Nota: Para enviar con imagen, usar form-data en Postman/Insomnia
POST {{baseUrl}}/pitchs/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="rating"

5
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="size"

mediano
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="groundType"

césped sintético
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="roof"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

5000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="business"

1
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="cancha.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./cancha.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### PATCH - Update Pitch (requiere autenticación admin o business_owner)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/pitchs/update/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="rating"

4
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

6000
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### DELETE - Remove Pitch (requiere autenticación admin o business_owner)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/pitchs/remove/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
